{"tid":1800412,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"AC米蘭宣布伊巴謙莫域加盟　效力半年","createTime":"2019-12-27T18:56:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-29T12:42:14.000Z","uid":79562,"like":30,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":40,"replies":[{"pid":"80356ac5207fce685f69248665c733bfeedb317a","tid":1800412,"uid":79562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T18:56:14.000Z","msg":"AC米蘭宣布伊巴謙莫域加盟　效力半年<br />\n<br />\n意甲球會AC米蘭宣布，與38歲的瑞典球星伊巴謙莫域簽約半年。伊巴謙莫域在2010至2012年，效力過AC米蘭，伊巴謙莫域之後轉會至巴黎聖日耳門及曼聯，再轉戰美職聯洛杉磯銀河。AC米蘭今屆表現令人失望，目前在聯賽只排在11位。<br />\n<br />\n2019-12-28 02:43:55"},{"pid":"c0d1943c7ee6096e764cc6811c501f7ca9ed3aa4","tid":1800412,"uid":79562,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T18:57:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1mnrCtM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1mnrCtM.png&h=5a520e46&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"907e261e76074eb7d422abb36d1fbaf5369a5c73","tid":1800412,"uid":261505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T18:58:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a1953ce416679a7d3a0b348eadf6167a92863f8","tid":1800412,"uid":130398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T19:10:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8886a0976ce3b32999ef124a2aed627ebcf5c3a6","tid":1800412,"uid":4156,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T19:14:32.000Z","msg":"返意甲養佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"044bf8e005a71eaafa88834b79e0672015373b89","tid":1800412,"uid":7854,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T19:22:59.000Z","msg":"入唔到波就好笑了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"848c05a1b7985d4b43dae697cf9a11ba93534395","tid":1800412,"uid":343033,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T20:12:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8